    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but rebuilding sounds like such a joke. why would i want to start over as a ghost? everyone thinks i'm someone i'm not, and the truth is just... exhausting. it feels more honest to just stop. to stop the pretending, the struggling, the trying to find meaning where there isn't any. isn't there just a certain peace in finally admitting it's over?",
